Package: biostatAnki
Type: Package
Title: Interactive BioStatistics Quiz via Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jorge", "Alcantara", email = "jorge.alcantara.espinosa@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Jorge Alcantara < 
Description: Provides a Shiny application presenting 50 biostatistics questions
    in an Anki-like format. Users write R code to answer each question,
    and the app evaluates the result against the expected output. The
    questions cover descriptive statistics, correlation, and simple linear
    regression. Shiny's reactive programming model automatically updates
    feedback when users submit their answers.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: shiny
